{"tid":2130144,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登筆記意外透露副總統人選或為女參議員賀錦麗","createTime":"2020-07-29T05:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T06:14:24.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"5530267fefd29de005f729faa63a862ad7f71854","tid":2130144,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/07/29/phpkZUolq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F07%2F29%2FphpkZUolq.jpg&h=aafaeefd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國民主黨總統大選參選人拜登（Joe Biden）28日稍早舉行第3場大型記者會，儘管拜登稱副選人手下週才會正式公佈，但有媒體意外捕捉到拜登的筆記，開頭第一行字寫的名字就是參議員賀錦麗（Kamala Harris），更在下方列出5大重點。<br />\n<br />\n據《CNN》報導，這5項重點就接在賀錦麗名字的下方，包括「不要懷恨在心」、「過去曾與我和吉兒一起競選活動」、「有才華」、「對競選有很大幫助」和「對她存有敬意」等，意外引發媒體關注，但拜登競選團隊拒絕回應這項消息。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n《CNN》提及，拜登在28日的記者會中堅持，副手人選要等下週才會公佈。外界認為，賀錦麗依然是目前呼聲最高的副手人選，但最後的關鍵在於，賀錦麗與拜登是否已修補了辯論攻擊的傷害，而賀錦麗還有另一層不可忽視的關係，她過去是拜登已逝世長子、前德拉瓦州（Delaware）總檢察長波‧拜登（Beau Biden）的好友。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3242975\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3242975&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6fG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=b3bb68b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3242975&h=768d140d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3242975</a>"},{"pid":"1a8e920842c073f6178a30eca1395e0c38db5627","tid":2130144,"uid":20170,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"屌你又玩政治政確<br />\n女人+非裔無撚敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6987c81e536ea4987c258781581afbf0f417fec","tid":2130144,"uid":127575,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:16:42.000Z","msg":"賀錦麗撐香港的"},{"pid":"67859bc24f795f1fe59a30634dbb00a35ca2a